<para>Procedures for environmental control will be explained in this
Primary Sidehead.</para>
<subpara1><title>Control of Environment</title><para>If this manual
contains items that need environmental control procedures, those procedures
will be explain in detail to protect the integrality of those items.</para>
</subpara1>
</envcont>
<warrprov><title> Warranty Provisions</title>
<para>For items cover by warranty information will be provided on
how to handle those items.</para>
<subpara1><title>How to Handle Warranty Items</title><para>Warranty
items will be sent to the equipment manufacture for repair.</para>
</subpara1>
</warrprov>
<tmimprep applicref="c"><title> Technical Manual Improvement Report
Preparation</title>
<subpara1><title>IMPROVEMENT REPORTS</title><para>Recommendations
for improvements to this technical order shall be submitted on AFTO
Form 22, Technical Manual (TM) Change Recommendation and Reply. Complete
AFTO Form 22 in accordance with TO 00-5-1.</para>
</subpara1>
</tmimprep>
