<applicdef><title>List of Applicability and Effectivity</title>
<para>In this example the &ldquo;TERM&rdquo; heading is used to define
the column used for the symbol. The &ldquo;DEFINITION&rdquo; heading
is used to define the applicability/effectivity for the symbol used
in the &ldquo;TERM&rdquo; column.</para>
<applichd>
<term>TERM</term><def>DEFINITION</def>
</applichd>
